## Verification Commands

### Check Your Rules Setup

```bash
# List all rule files
find . -name .cursor -type d

# Check for legacy format (should not exist)
ls -la .cursorrules/
# Should return No such file or directory

# Verify nested rules structure
tree -L 3 -I 'node_modules' -I 'dist' -a . | grep .cursor

# Count rules per location
find . -path */.cursor/rules/*.mdc | wc -l
```

### Test Glob Patterns

```bash
# Test if a glob pattern matches files (from rule directory)
cd packages/levva-agent/.cursor/rules/
find ../.. -path src/actions/**/*.ts | head -5

# Should return actual TypeScript files
```

